short_description: Maricic Law Firm is a Temecula-based personal injury law practice founded by local attorney Dustin Maricic, focusing on car accidents, dog bites, and maximum client compensation through personalized service.
long_description: Established in 2010, Maricic Law Firm prioritizes quality over quantity, with Attorney Dustin Maricic personally handling cases instead of delegating to case managers. The firm serves Riverside County clients in areas like Temecula, Murrieta, and Menifee, recovering millions in settlements (e.g., $500K, $900K, $1.3M, up to $10M verdicts). Clients praise Dustin's direct involvement, negotiation skills reducing medical bills, and forcing insurers to accept full fault.
service_areas: Temecula, Murrieta, Canyon Lake, Sun City, Winchester, Wildomar, Menifee, Riverside, and surrounding areas in Southern California, including San Diego and Los Angeles regions.
